creator: Serhii Lyzun
descriptionHtml:
TapeMeet is the right place, where you can find your soul, friend, partner, family, and fun. You can choose your sympathy not by photo, but by video, which helps you understand much more about this person: emotion, voice, feeling, etc... Like in real life!

You can specify yourself via avatar and a short video. While registration try to record a meaningful short 10 seconds video with voice and point out your best traits.

Use swiping to the right or Like Button to like a person, to the left or Unlike Button to unlike a person, to the top or Super-Like button to super-like a person.

If someone likes you back, it's a match. You can chat with your match, meet up in the real world, and find something new.

Currently, this App is in an active phase of development, but all main features are ready to use and fully free. Enjoy it.

descriptionHtml:
TapeMeet: Free App for Online Relationships. Make videos, and chat for free. Discover love on our easy and intuitive app.
❤️🎥 TapeMeet: An Odyssey of Online Love 🌃💏
In a world where connections are essential, TapeMeet Video stands out as a unique platform, providing an unparalleled journey toward true love. Our commitment is to transform the landscape of online dating, combining innovative technology with an authentic approach.
At the heart of TapeMeet is the revolutionary Video Dating feature. We believe a video speaks louder than a thousand words, so we offer our users the opportunity to create captivating video profiles. Now, your online interactions will transcend superficiality, allowing you to see and be seen in a way that goes beyond conventional photographs. ❤️🎥 🌹🥂
To highlight authenticity in online interactions, TapeMeet Video emphasizes the importance of solid communication. Flirt, chat, and discover real connections while enjoying the intimacy only video can offer. 💏🔍📢
🌟 TapeMeet Video App: Free Online Dating 💑📱
Sometimes, all we need is a spark to ignite the flames of a relationship. With Video profiles, we introduce a revolutionary approach to online dating, combining the convenience of an app with the authenticity of video. This is your invitation to an exciting journey in search of true love.
Key Features:
Authentic Video Dates 🎥💖
Become the director of your love story. Instead of relying solely on static photos, users can create dynamic profiles with videos that capture their unique personalities.
2. Online and Free Chat 💬🔓
We've eliminated financial barriers to ensure everyone has access to true love. Video communication is completely free, allowing unrestricted online chats.
3. Detailed and Personalized Profiles 🌐👫
Our app allows users to detail their preferences, hobbies, and values, making it easier to find compatible partners. TapeMeet Video's advanced algorithm connects people based on common interests.
4. User-Friendly with Our Intuitive App 📱🚀
Navigate effortlessly with an intuitive user interface. TapeMeet Video is designed to be accessible to everyone, from singles to those seeking serious relationships.
5. Safe and Respectful Online Dating 🔐💼
We prioritize safety and respect. Moderation tools and privacy features ensure your experience on TapeMeet Video is always positive and protected.
TapeMeet Video is more than an app; it's a community where hearts meet. Download now and discover a new way to connect online. Here, love is free, authentic, and just a video away. 💑🌟
In the pursuit of love, we celebrate diversity! In our community, people of different genders and ages find authentic connections. Connect with lesbians, gays, and LGBTQ+ community members. Find love at any age, whether you're 30, 40, or 50. Here, love transcends barriers, uniting diverse hearts in one passion.
TapeMeet Video: Video Dating and Chat App. Meet singles, schedule dates, and explore a new era of online dating.
